verbose_text: These data are in keeping with the work of Vandraas et al., who identified an inverse association between HG and sPTB (< 32 weeks) when analyzing the Medical Birth Registry of Norway.12 In contrast, previous studies show correlations between HG and an increased risk of PTB,9, 10, 21 which may be explained by their heterogeneous definitions of HG12 and their inclusion of all PTB, both iatrogenic and spontaneous.
